We are going to see how zodiac signs are divided into different categories according to its character and nature.

First let us see odd and even signs,
1. The sign Aries(Mesha) is odd Sign
2. The sign Taurus(Vrishabha) is even Sign
3. The sign Gemini(Mithuna) is odd Sign
4. The sign Cancer(Kataka) is even Sign
5. The sign Leo(Simha) is odd Sign
6. The sign Virgo(Kanya) is even Sign
7. The sign Libra(Thula) is odd Sign
8. The sign Scorpio(Vrichika) is even Sign
9. The sign Sagittarius(Dhanus) is odd Sign
10. The sign Capricorn(Makara) is even Sign
11. The sign Aquarius(Kumbha) is odd Sign
12. The sign Pisces(Meena) is even Sign

The next we will see male sign and female sign, basically all odd sign are male signs and all even signs are female signs.

1. The sign Aries(Mesha) is male Sign
2. The sign Taurus(Vrishabha) is female Sign

10. The sign Capricorn(Makara) is female Sign
11. The sign Aquarius(Kumbha) is male Sign
12. The sign Pisces(Meena) is female Sign

The we will see Movable signs, Fixed Signs, and Common signs. 

The movable signs of the Zodiac have a moving nature hence called movable signs. The fixed signs of the zodiac will have a fixed nature and hence called as fixed sign. The common sign will have both movable and fixed characteristics and hence referred as Dual signs

1. The sign Aries(Mesha) is movable Sign
2. The sign Taurus(Vrishabha) is fixed Sign
3. The sign Gemini(Mithuna) is common Sign
4. The sign Cancer(Kataka) is movable Sign
